Interface HasSourceEntity

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface HasSourceEntity
Represents something with a source entity. For example, the caster of an ability, or whoever applied a buff.

    • getSource

      XivCombatant getSource()
      Returns:
      The source of this action. Note that this is a snapshot of the source at the point in time when the action occurred. To see the current data, use XivState.getLatestCombatantData(XivCombatant).
